ou%20get%20laid%20off%2C%20one%20of%20the%20first%20things%20you%20should%20do%20is%20volunteer%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223206%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22virginia%20beach%20volunteering%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5df7e42479d75715a74e3d8b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222145%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAccording%20to%20one%20recruiter%2C%20volunteering%20when%20you're%20out%20of%20work%20can%20help%20structure%20your%20day%20and%20put%20the%20challenges%20you're%20facing%20in%20context.%3Cp%3ELynne%20Sladky%2FAP%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EVolunteering%20can%20help%20job%20seekers%20find%20gratitude%20and%20purpose%2C%20according%20to%20one%20recruiter.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHelping%20someone%20else%20also%20offers%20structure%20and%20can%20support%20mental%20health%20during%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwent-through-a-dozen-interviews-didnt-get-the-job-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edifficult%20job%20hunts%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ENetworking%20and%20skill-building%20are%20crucial%2C%20but%20you%20can%20also%20discuss%20your%20volunteering%20in%20interviews.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-to-say-in-interview-after-you-have-been-fired-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elose%20your%20job%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it%20can%20feel%20like%20the%20end%20of%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20possible%20balm%3A%20volunteering.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeeing%20what%20others%20might%20be%20going%20through%20can%20help%20the%20newly%20jobless%20size%20up%20their%20own%20problems%2C%20according%20to%20Jennifer%20Schielke%2C%20CEO%20of%20the%20staffing%20firm%20Summit%20Group%20Solutions%20and%20author%20of%20%26quot%3BLeading%20for%20Impact.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20have%20time%20to%20volunteer%2C%20go%20do%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20Business%20Insider%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BGo%20get%20some%20encouragement%20by%20sitting%20alongside%20someone%20who%20has%20it%20worse%20than%20you%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVolunteering%20can%20be%20one%20way%20to%20find%20gratitude%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20help%20people%20navigate%20the%20steps%20needed%20to%20land%20a%20new%20role%2C%20Schielke%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20volunteering%20shouldn't%20replace%20other%20must-dos%20%E2%80%94%20like%20building%20up%20your%20skills%2C%20turning%20to%20your%20network%20to%20help%20you%20find%20a%20role%2C%20and%20beefing%20up%20your%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20%E2%80%94%20it%20could%20offer%20a%20brief%20respite%20from%20some%20of%20the%20stress%20accompanying%20a%20job%20search.%20That's%20important%20because%20while%20the%20overall%20labor%20market%20remains%20strong%2C%20many%20employers%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpeople-looking-for-jobs-enduring-many-rounds-of-interviews-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etaking%20longer%20to%20hire%3C%2Fa%3E.%20That%20means%20the%20hunt%20for%20what's%20next%20could%20be%20more%20protracted%20than%20many%20job%20seekers%20might%20like.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECommitting%20to%20doing%20some%20work%20for%20others%20can%20also%20help%20retain%20structure%20in%20your%20schedule%20when%20work%20hours%20disappear%2C%20Schielke%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYour%20days%20still%20have%20meaning%20and%20purpose%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BThat's%20going%20to%20keep%20you%20upbeat.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESchielke%20said%20beyond%20the%20intrinsic%20benefits%20of%20volunteering%2C%20those%20efforts%20can%20give%20you%20something%20to%20talk%20about%20in%20a%20job%20interview%20when%20asked%20about%20the%20things%20you%20might%20have%20done%20since%20your%20last%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20really%20a%20time%20where%20you%20can%20show%20yourself%20as%20different%20by%20showcasing%20your%20character%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2216444c4b-e711-41c8-b39c-fc0d96d9644b%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ETurn%20to%20your%20network%20for%20help%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOutside%20of%20seeing%20how%20you%20might%20help%20others%2C%20there%20are%20other%20steps%20you%20can%20take%20if%20you're%20newly%20unemployed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESchielke%20said%20it's%20important%20to%20have%20a%20sounding%20board%20to%20help%20you%20remain%20accountable%20for%20your%20next%20actions%2C%20especially%20as%20getting%20laid%20off%20can%20be%20a%20shock.%20She%20pointed%20to%20the%20job%20cuts%20that%20hit%20the%20tech%20industry%20in%20recent%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20know%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20didn't%20think%20it%20would%20be%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20Having%20people%20you%20can%20talk%20through%20the%20situation%20with%20can%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESchielke%20said%20that%20newly%20jobless%20people%20sometimes%20need%20to%20separate%20what%20they%20want%20from%20what%20they%20need.%20Job%20seekers%20who%20are%20inflexible%20and%20insist%20on%20remote%20work%20or%20attaining%20a%20certain%20salary%20might%20find%20it%20harder%20to%20get%20a%20new%20gig.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20real%20reality%20check%20and%20maybe%20a%20piece%20of%20humble%20pie%20that%20has%20to%20be%20taken%20in%2C%26quot%3B%20Schielke%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20crucial%20to%20consider%20how%20people%20in%20your%20network%20can%20help%20you%20look%20for%20something%20new%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBeing%20able%20to%20connect%20with%20a%20person%20or%20know%20someone%20who%20knows%20someone%20who%20can%20get%20your%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20in%20front%20of%20the%20right%20people%20is%20so%20important%2C%26quot%3B%20Schielke%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20it's%20even%20more%20critical%20now%20to%20turn%20to%20your%20network%20because%20the%20ease%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-your-resum