2C%20has%20defended%20her%20against%20a%20derogatory%20comment%20made%20by%20JD%20Vance%2C%20the%20running-mate%20of%20Republican%20nominee%20Donald%20Trump.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVance%20called%20Harris%20a%20%26quot%3Bchildless%20cat%20lady%26quot%3B%20in%20a%202021%20interview%2C%20which%20resurfaced%20after%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20recently%20endorsed%20Harris%20as%20the%20Democratic%20presidential%20nominee.%20Ms%20Emhoff%20swiftly%20responded%20to%20the%20remark%20on%20her%20Instagram%20Stories%2C%20writing%2C%20%26quot%3BHow%20can%20you%20be%20'childless'%20when%20you%20have%20cutie%20pie%20kids%20like%20Cole%20and%20I%3F%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20love%20my%20three%20parents.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKerstin%20Emhoff%2C%20Ella's%20mother%2C%20also%20spoke%20out%20against%20JD%20Vance's%20attacks%20on%20Kamala%20Harris%2C%20calling%20them%20%26quot%3Bbaseless%26quot%3B.%20In%20a%20statement%20to%20NBC%20News%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BFor%20over%2010%20years%2C%20since%20Cole%20and%20Ella%20were%20teenagers%2C%20Kamala%20has%20been%20a%20co-parent%20with%20Doug%20and%20me.%20She%20is%20loving%2C%20nurturing%2C%20fiercely%20protective%2C%20and%20always%20present.%20I%20love%20our%20blended%20family%20and%20am%20grateful%20to%20have%20her%20in%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20is%20Ella%20Emhoff%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElla%20Emhoff%2C%2025%2C%20is%20the%20daughter%20of%20Douglas%20Emhoff%20and%20Kerstin%20Emhoff%2C%20and%20the%20stepdaughter%20of%20Kamala%20Harris.%20She%20was%2015%20when%20her%20father%20married%20Harris%20in%202014%2C%20and%20has%20since%20considered%20her%20a%20third%20parent%2C%20affectionately%20calling%20her%20%26quot%3BMomala%26quot%3B.%20Ella%20and%20her%20older%20brother%2C%20Cole%2C%20were%20named%20after%20jazz%20legends%20Ella%20Fitzgerald%20and%20Cole%20Porter.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Emhoff%2C%20a%20Parsons%20fashion%20student%2