dia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fmystery-bones-tied-to-wwii-war-crimes-still-unsolved-activists-demand-answers%2Famp_articleshow%2F112036624.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fmystery-bones-tied-to-wwii-war-crimes-still-unsolved-activists-demand-answers%2Famp_articleshow%2F112036624.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tattooed%20Enemy%20Names%20On%20Spa%20Murder%20Victim%20Help%20Cops%20Arrest%20Suspects%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EGuru%20Waghmare%2C%20who%20was%20murdered%20at%20a%20spa%20had%20tattooed%20the%20names%20of%2022%20persons%20who%20could%20potentially%20harm%20him%2C%20police%20said%20on%20Thursday%20as%20they%20arrested%20at%20least%20three%20suspects%20a%20day%20after%20the%20crime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20name%20of%20spa%20owner%20Santosh%20Sherekar%2C%20one%20of%20those%20arrested%2C%20was%20among%20these%2022%20persons%2C%20said%20a%20police%20official.%20Besides%20him%2C%20the%20two%20alleged%20assailants%20were%20also%20arrested%20and%20two%20more%20persons%20were%20arrested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWaghmare%20(48)%2C%20who%20claimed%20to%20be%20a%20Right%20to%20Information%20activist%20but%20had%20several%20criminal%20cases%20registered%20against%20him%2C%20was%20killed%20at%20Soft%20Touch%20Spa%20in%20central%20Mumbai's%20Worli%20in%20the%20early%20hours%20of%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20autopsy%2C%20it%20was%20found%20that%20he%20had%20inscribed%20the%20names%20of%20his%20potential%20enemies%20on%20his%20thighs%2C%20the%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESherekar%2C%20owner%20of%20the%20spa%2C%20had%20allegedly%20given%20'supari'%20or%20contract%20for%20killing%20Waghmare%20as%20he%20was%20fed%20up%20with%20Waghmare's%20extortion%20threats%2C%20the%20police%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20allegedly%20paid%20Rs%206%20lakh%20to%20Mohammed%20Feroze%20Ansari%20(26)%20to%20kill%20Waghmare.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnsari%20and%20Sherekar%20knew%20each%20other%20as%20Ansari%20also%20ran%20a%20spa%20at%20Nallasopara%20near%20Mumbai%20which%20was%20shut%20down%20due%20to%20a%20raid%20last%20year.%20The%20raid%20had%20followed%20Waghmare's%20complaint%20to%20the%20authorities%2C%20the%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnsari%20approached%20Sherekar%20seeking%20to%20stop%20Waghmare%20from%20filing%20such%20complaints%20and%20extorting%20money%20from%20spa%20owners.%20Sherekar%20allegedly%20asked%20him%20to%20have%20Waghmare%20eliminated%2C%20the%20police%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnsari%20then%20contacted%20Saquib%20Ansari%2C%20a%20Delhi%20resident%2C%20and%20the%20conspiracy%20was%20hatched%20three%20months%20ago%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20conducting%20a%20recce%20and%20studying%20Waghmare's%20routine%20for%20three%20months%2C%20the%20accused%20planned%20to%20kill%20him%20at%20Sherekar's%20spa%2C%20the%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECCTV%20footage%20outside%20a%20liquor%20bar%20in%20Sion%20where%20Waghmare%20had%20celebrated%20his%20birthday%20with%20his%2021-year-old%20girlfriend%20on%20Tuesday%20evening%20showed%20that%20the%20two%20assailants%2C%20wearing%20raincoats%2C%20were%20tailing%20him%20there.%20The%20duo%20followed%20Waghmare%20to%20Sherekar's%20spa%20on%20a%20scooter%20later%20that%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20found%20that%20one%20of%20the%20assailants%20bought%20two%20gutka%20packets%20from%20a%20paan%20shop%20near%20the%20liquor%20bar%2C%20paying%20through%20a%20UPI%20system.%20UPI%20record%20showed%20that%20his%20name%20was%20Mohammed%20Feroze%20Ansari.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESherekar%20had%20received%20multiple%20calls%20from%20the%20phone%20number%20linked%20to%20Ansari's%20UPI%20ID%2C%20the%20investigation%20found.%20It%20established%20the%20link%20between%20the%20two.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFeroze%20and%20Saquib%20Ansari%20entered%20the%20spa%20around%201.30%20am%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20took%20Waghmare's%20girlfriend%20to%20another%20room%2C%20and%20then%20allegedly%20murdered%20Waghmare%20using%20the%20separated%20blades%20of%20a%20pair%20of%20scissors%20costing%20Rs%207%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20blades%20was%20used%20to%20slit%20his%20throat%2C%20while%20the%20other%20was%20used%20to%20stab%20him%20in%20the%20stomach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWaghmare's%20girlfriend%20claimed%20to%20have%20learnt%20about%20the%20murder%20only%20at%209.30%20in%20the%20morning%20and%20informed%20Sherekar%2C%20who%20took%20over%20two%20hours%20to%20inform%20the%20police%2C%20the%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20had%20already%20detained%20Sherekar%20for%20questioning%2C%20and%20put%20him%20under%20arrest%20after%20interrogation%20throughout%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFeroze%20Ansari%20was%20subsequently%20arrested%20by%20a%20crime%20branch%20team%20from%20suburban%20Nalasopara%2C%20while%20Saquib%20Ansari%20was%20picked%20up%20from%20Kota%20in%20Rajasthan%20en-route%20to%20New%20Delhi%20along%20with%20two%20more%20people%20who%20were%20suspected%20to%20be%20involved%20in%20the%20conspiracy%2C%20the%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20total%20of%20five%20people%2C%20thus%2C%20have%20been%20arrested%20%2C%20the%20official%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20they%20are%20also%20probing%20the%20role%20of%20Waghmare's%20girlfriend.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20arrested%20accused%20(Saquib)%20was%20being%20brought%20to%20Mumbai%20after%20he%20was%20caught%20on%20the%20Garibrath%20Express%20near%20Kota%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20along%20with%20two%20more%20suspects%2C%20said%20DCP%20(detection)%20Datta%20Nalawade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWaghmare%20allegedly%20used%20to%20extort%20money%20from%20spa%20owners%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20Navi%20Mumbai%2C%20Thane%2C%20and%20Palghar%20from%202010%20and%20had%20criminal%20cases%20of%20extortion%2C%20rape%20and%20molestation%20registered%20against%20him%2C%20another%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20eight%20cognisable%20offences%20and%2022%20non-cognisab