rt%20and%20resilient%20attributes.%20This%20comes%20amid%20the%20transition%20phase%20following%20Rohit%20Sharma's%20retirement%20from%20T20Is%2C%20with%20Suryakumar%20Yadav%20and%20Hardik%20Pandya%20being%20considered%20potential%20successors.%20Bumrah%20was%20a%20part%20of%20discussions%20about%20the%20new%20captaincy%2C%20but%20was%20ultimately%20handed%20the%20role%20to%20Yadav.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SPORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Findia-in-sri-lanka%2Fi-cannot-go-to-the-team-and-tell-jasprit-bumrah-makes-a-blunt-above-my-pay-grade-remark-on-captaincy-ambitions%2Farticleshow%2F112035475.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Taiwan%20Olympic%20Legend%20Finds%20Her%20Life%20Story%20In%20Aamir%20Khan's%20'Dangal'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20watched%20Dangal%20with%20Chinese%20subtitles%20a%20few%20years%20ago%2C%20I%20noticed%20an%20uncanny%20resemblance%20between%20the%20wrestlers'%20father%20and%20my%20own%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Chen%20Shih-hsin%2C%20Taiwan's%20first-ever%20Olympic%20gold%20medallist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChen%20clinched%20gold%20in%20the%20women's%20flyweight%20division%20(49-kilogram%20category)%20in%20Taekwondo%20at%20the%202004%20Athens%20Olympics%2C%20ending%20a%2072-year-long%20gold%20medal%20drought%20for%20Taiwan.%20Despite%20being%20a%20self-governing%20democracy%20with%20its%20own%20constitution%20and%20legislature%2C%20Taiwan%20competes%20at%20the%20Olympics%20under%20the%20fictitious%20name%20%26quot%3BChinese%20Taipei%26quot%3B%20-%20it%20is%20neither%20part%20of%20China%20nor%20comprised%20solely%20of%20the%20city%20of%20Taipei%20(which%20is%20one%20of%20the%2023%20cities%20in%20the%20island%20nation).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20father%20was%20a%20hard%20taskmaster%2C%20much%20like%20the%20father%20portrayed%20in%20the%20film.%20I%20feel%20he%20was%20even%20tougher%20on%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20shares%20Chen%20as%20she%20teaches%20around%20100%20children%20at%20her%20Taekwondo%20school%20in%20the%20rural%20township%20of%20Xinfeng%2C%20near%20Taiwan's%20semiconductor%20hub%2C%20Hsinchu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYes%2C%20you%20could%20call%20me%20a%20chip%20off%20the%20old%20block%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20inheriting%20my%20father's%20grit%20and%20toughness%2C%20similar%20to%20the%20characters%20in%20Dangal%2C%26quot%3B%20admits%20Chen%2C%20whose%20life%20story%20is%20full%20of%20dramatic%20and%20emotional%20twists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20is%20half-aboriginal%2C%20as%20her%20mother%20is%20from%20Taiwan's%20indigenous%20Atayal%20community.%20Her%20father%2C%20Chen%20Wei-hsiung%2C%20ran%20a%20Taekwondo%20training%20centre%20in%20Taipei%20and%20introduced%20her%20to%20martial%20arts%20at%20the%20age%20of%20five.%20By%2015%2C%20Chen%20had%20already%20made%20a%20mark%20on%20the%20world%20stage%20by%20winning%20her%20debut%20appearance%20at%20the%20World%20Cup%20in%20the%20Cayman%20Islands%20in%201994.%20Two%20years%20later%2C%20she%20secured%20her%20second%20world%20title%20in%20Brazil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20her%20career%20took%20an%20unexpected%20turn%20shortly%20after.%20%26quot%3BI%20used%20to%20despise%20my%20father's%20relentless%20push.%20One%20day%2C%20at%2018%2C%20I%20argued%20with%20him%20and%20ran%20away%20from%20home%2C%26quot%3B%20Chen%20reveals%2C%20recalling%20her%20transformation%20from%20world%20champion%20to%20a%20%26quot%3Bbetel%20nut%20beauty%26quot%3B%20-%20a%20term%20for%20scantily-clad%20young%20women%20who%20sold%20betel%20nuts%20at%20kiosks%20across%20Taiwan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20leaving%20her%20family%20and%20Taekwondo%2C%20Chen%20survived%20by%20vending%20betel%20nuts%20and%20other%20products%20in%20Taichung.%20%26quot%3BI%20felt%20like%20a%20rebel%2C%20much%20like%20the%20girl%20in%20the%20Bollywood%20movie%20who%20rebelled%20after%20joining%20the%20national%20team.%20But%20unlike%20her%20outspoken%20defiance%2C%20I%20simply%20left%2C%26quot%3B%20shares%20Chen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20years%20later%2C%20a%20poignant%20line%20in%20a%20radio%20advertisement%20about%20a%20son%20unable%20to%20care%20for%20his%20ageing%20parents%20on%20their%20birthday%20led%20her%20to%20return%20home.%20Reuniting%20with%20her%20father%2C%20she%20pledged%20to%20resume%20her%20training%20and%20pursue%20an%20Olympic%20dream%20together.%20However%2C%20the%20three%20lost%20years%20cost%20her%20a%20chance%20to%20compete%20in%20the%202000%20Sydney%20Olympics%2C%20where%20Taekwondo%20debuted%20as%20an%20Olympic%20medal%20sport.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBeing%20on%20my%20own%20for%20those%20three%20years%20strengthened%20me%2C%20helping%20me%20cope%20with%20the%20disappointment%20of%20missing%20the%20Sydney%20Games%2C%26quot%3B%20Chen%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20indomitable%20spirit%20and%20her%20father's%20unwavering%20support%20fuelled%20her%20strenuous%20preparation%20for%20the%20next%20four%20years.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20reached%20Athens%2C%20my%20biggest%20adversary%20was%20myself%2C%20not%20my%20rivals%20from%20Cuba%2C%20Nepal%2C%20Canada%2C%20or%20Nicaragua%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20reflects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Olympic%20gold%20was%20our%20shared%20dream.%26quot%3B%20Chen%20continues%2C%20%26quot%3BOpening%20a%20Taekwondo%20gym%20and%20running%20it%20for%20decades%20was%20as%20much%20my%20father's%20goal%20as%20it%20was%20mine.%20His%20ultimate%20aim%20was%20to%20bring%20an%20Olympic%20gold%20medal%20to%20the%20gym.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20August%2026%2C%20Chen%20made%20history%20by%20defeating%20Cuban%20opponent%20Yanelis%20Labrada%20to%20win%20the%20first-ever%20gold%20medal%20for%20her%20%26quot%3Binvisible%26quot%3B%20nation%2C%20herself%2C%20and%20most%20importantly%2C%20her%20father.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOver%20the%20years%2C%20I've%20fought%20countless%20matches%2C%20shed%20many%20tears%2C%20and%20accumulated%20numerous%20injuries.%20That%20final%20match%20in%20Athens%20was%20worth%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20expresses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%2025%2C%20Chen%20decided%20to%20retire.%20%26quot%3BThese%20past%20twenty-odd%20years%20have%20been%20challenging%2C%20but%20I've%20been%20fortunate%20to%20avoid%20severe%20injuries%20thanks%20to%20my%20father's%20meticulous%20training%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20achieving%20her%20Olympic%20dream%2C%20Chen's%20life%20continued%20to%20resemble%20a%20gripping%20film%20script.%20She%20pursued%20a%20PhD%20in%20sports%20psychology%2C%20secured%20a%20position%20as%20an%20associate%20professor%20at%20a%20leading%20university%2C%20and%20started%20a%20family%20with%20two%20children.%20However%2C%20personal%20turmoil%20struck%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20alleged%20extramarital%20affair%20with%20a%20fellow%20coach%20tarnished%20her%20reputation%2C%20forcing%20her%20to%20resign%20from%20her%20university%20post%2C%20leave%20her%20home%2C%20and%20yield%20custody%20of%20her%20daughter%20to%20her%20estranged%20husband.%20Yet%2C%20Chen%20rose%20from%20the%20ashes%2C%20relocating%20to%20Xinfeng%20with%20her%20son.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Chen%20teaches%20Taekwondo%20to%20local%20children%20in%20her%20self-established%20dojang%2C%20away%20from%20the%20public%20eye%20and%20the%20bustle%20of%20Taipei.%20Although%20her%20Athens%20Olympic%20gold%20medal%20resides%20at%20her%20father's%20home%2C%20she%20now%20dreams%20of%20earning%20a%20gold%20medal%20for%20her%20Taekwondo%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Suvam%20Pal%20works%20for%20the%20Taipei-based%20TaiwanPlus%20news%20channel)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721978700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fc69in8e8_chen-shih-hsin_625x300_26_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fexclusive-taiwan-olympic-legend-finds-her-life-story-in-aamir-khan-dangal-