e%20has%20not%20made%20an%20official%20statement%2C%20their%20cryptic%20posts%20on%20social%20media%20have%20been%20making%20headline%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fmalaika-arora-shares-another-cryptic-post-amid-breakup-rumours-with-arjun-kapoor-saysevery-kind-action-is-a-%2Farticleshow%2F112035653.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Wipe%20it%20off%20the%20face%20of%20the%20Earth'%3A%20Donald%20Trump%20calls%20for%20obliteration%20of%20Iran%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721977356000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-112036911%2Cimgsize-875818.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fwipe-it-off-the-face-of-the-earth-donald-trump-calls-for-obliteration-of-iran%2Farticleshow%2F112035624.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F112035624.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fwipe-it-off-the-face-of-the-earth-donald-trump-calls-for-obliteration-of-iran%2Farticleshow%2F112035624.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fwipe-it-off-the-face-of-the-earth-donald-trump-calls-for-obliteration-of-iran%2Famp_articleshow%2F112035624.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fwipe-it-off-the-face-of-the-earth-donald-trump-calls-for-obliteration-of-iran%2Famp_articleshow%2F112035624.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2240%20Years%20After%20Bhopal%20Tragedy%2C%20Disposal%20Of%20Toxic%20Waste%20Poses%20Cancer%20Threat%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForty%20years%20after%20the%20Bhopal%20gas%20tragedy%2C%20its%20toxic%20waste%20cocktail%20is%20brewing%20afresh.%20About%20350%20metric%20tons%20of%20hazardous%20waste%20from%20the%20Union%20Carbide%20factory%20is%20set%20to%20be%20disposed%20of%20at%20the%20Treatment%20Storage%20Disposal%20Facility%20in%20Pithampur%2C%20Indore.%20The%20facility%2C%20though%2C%20has%20failed%20six%20previous%20tests%20on%20whether%20it%20can%20contain%20the%20emission%20which%20poses%20a%20significant%20cancer%20risk.%20And%20the%20cost%20will%20be%20far%20higher.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwelve%20years%20ago%2C%20a%20German%20company%2C%20GIZ%2C%20offered%20to%20cart%20off%20the%20waste%20to%20Germany%20and%20dispose%20of%20it%20for%20Rs%2022%20crore.%20Disposing%20of%20the%20waste%20will%20now%20cost%20Rs%20126%20crore%20--%20six-times%20the%20previous%20estimate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cost%20to%20health%20could%20be%20beyond%20math.%20The%20quantity%20to%20be%20disposed%20represents%20just%205%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20total%20hazardous%20waste.%20But%20experts%20have%20warned%20that%20it%20could%20release%20large%20amounts%20of%20organochlorine%2C%20dioxins%2C%20and%20furans%20--%20carcinogenic%20chemicals%20that%20are%20extremely%20harmful%20to%20humans%20and%20the%20environment.%20The%20incineration%20site%20in%20Pithampur%20has%20several%20villages%20within%20a%20distance%20of%202%20km.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20World%20Health%20Organization%20has%20also%20warned%20that%20incineration%20at%20a%20faulty%20site%20could%20cause%20cancer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20past%2C%20we%20protested%20against%20burning%20this%20waste.%20The%20then%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20Environment%20Minister%20assured%20us%20it%20wouldn't%20happen%20here.%20Despite%20these%20assurances%2C%20the%20waste%20is%20now%20set%20to%20be%20incinerated%20in%20Pithampur%2C%20a%20process%20that%20will%20take%20six%20months.%20If%20this%20happens%2C%20we%20will%20protest%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Gautam%20Kothar%2C%20the%20coordinator%20of%20the%20Lok%20Maitri%20Sansthan%2C%20an%20NGO.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20plan%20has%20been%20in%20the%20pipeline%20for%20long.%20But%20in%202012%2C%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20government%20filed%20a%20petition%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20opposing%20it.%20The%20same%20year%2C%20at%20a%20cabinet%20meeting%20in%20Bhopal%2C%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20Babulal%20Gaur%20and%20then%20Environment%20Minister%20Jayant%20Malaiya%20strongly%20opposed%20incinerating%20the%20waste%20in%20Pithampur%2C%20fearing%20contamination%20of%20Yashwant%20Sagar%20Dam%20and%20Tarapura%20village.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20one%20was%20ready%20to%20take%20on%20the%20waste.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202007%2C%20Gujarat%20refused%20to%20incinerate%20Bhopal's%20waste%20despite%20financial%20incentives.%20In%202011%2C%20Maharashtra%20declined%20DRDO's%20proposal%20to%20incinerate%20the%20waste%20in%20Nagpur.%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20too%20refused%20to%20accept%20the%20waste.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20I%20became%20the%20minister%2C%20we%20took%20a%20budget%20from%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20for%20the%20waste.%20We%20are%20making%20efforts%20with%20the%20centre%2C%20working%20with%20the%20cooperation%20of%20the%20central%20government.%20Tenders%20were%20issued%20for%20its%20execution%20even%20before%20I%20became%20the%20minister.%20Our%20expectation%20is%20that%20all%20that%20the%20waste%20should%20be%20burnt%20within%20a%20year.%20There%20is%20a%20decision%20regarding%20burning%20of%20the%20waste%2C%20and%20we%20cannot%20do%20anything%20about%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Kunwar%20Vijay%20Shah%2C%20Minister%2C%20Gas%20Relief%20and%20Rehabilitation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELying%20for%2040%20years%2C%20the%20waste%20has%20contaminated%20soil%20and%20groundwater%20and%20pose%20a%20huge%20risk%20to%20generations.%20Data%20shows%20that%20from%202004%20to%202018%2C%20toxic%20waste%20polluted%20groundwater%20in%2042%20settlements%20around%20the%20Union%20Carbide%20factory.%20In%20the%20last%20five%20years%20alone%2C%20the%20contamination%20has%20spread%20to%2029%20more%20settlements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EDeaths%2C%20survival%2C%20and%20challenges%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20official%20figures%20of%20the%20death%20count%20vary%20-%20the%20central%20government%20pegs%20it%20at%205%2C295%20while%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20cites%2015%2C342%2C%20and%20the%20Indian%20Council%20of%20Medical%20Research%20(ICMR)%20estimates%20it%20to%20be%2025%2C000%20-%20the%20true%20extent%20of%20the%20tragedy%20goes%20beyond%20numbers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESurvivors%20are%20forced%20to%20live%20with%20the%20lingering%20effects%20of%20the%20disaster%2C%20facing%20health%20issues%20and%20inadequate%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20groundwater%20of%20Brij%20Vihar%20Colony%20--%20located%20around%203%20km%20from%20the%20Union%20Carbide%20factory%20--%20has%20been%20severely%20polluted%20by%20the%20factory's%20toxic%20waste.%20Arif%20Nagar%2C%20right%20across%20the%20Union%20Carbide%20factory%2C%20is%20still%20suffering%20from%20the%20aftereffects.%20Thousands%20of%20gas%20victims%2C%20their%20children%2C%20and%20grandchildren%20continue%20to%20be%20affected.%20Many%20children%20are%20born%20with%20mental%20and%20physical%20disabilities%2C%20and%20families%20cannot%20afford%20the%20necessary%20medical%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20water%20in%20the%20affected%20areas%20is%20so%20contaminated%20that%20it%20leaves%20white%20marks%20and%20crusts%20on%20buckets%20and%20coolers%20within%20weeks.%20Residents%20report%20an%20increase%20in%20diabetes%2C%20heart%20attacks%2C%20and%20other%20serious%20health%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%202004%20to%202018%2C%20toxic%20waste%20poisoned%20the%20groundwater%20of%2042%20settlements%20around%20the%20factory.%20Despite%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20order%20to%20provide%20clean%20water%2C%20the%20contamination%20has%20spread%20to%2029%20more%20settlements%20in%20the%20last%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20hard%20water%20caused%20me%20to%20have%20a%20heart%20attack%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Bhagwati%20Prasad%20Pandey%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Bhopal's%20Brij%20Vihar%20Colony.%20%26quot%3BMy%20family%20and%20the%20entire%20neighbourhood%20are%20suffering.%20The%20municipal%20corporation%20was%20ordered%20to%20provide%20clean%20water%2C%20but%20they%20refused%2C%20citing%20that%20it%20is%20a%20private%20colony.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSince%20this%20colony%20was%20built%2C%20the%20water%20has%20been%20contaminated.%20Tests%20revealed%20heavy%20metals.%20Drinking%20this%20water%20has%20caused%20gallbladder%20issues%2C%20kidney%20stones%2C%20and%20skin%20infections.%20Despite%20multiple%20complaints%2C%20the%20municipal%20corporation%20has%20not%20provided%20clean%20water%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20RS%20Pal%2C%20another%20resident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArif%20Nagar%20settlement%2C%20located%20right%20in%20front%20of%20Union%20Carbide%2C%20is%20a%20grim%20testament%20to%20the%20enduring%20impact%20of%20the%20disaster.%20Residents%20here%20continue%20to%20suffer%20from%20the%20contamination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmina%2C%20a%20resident%2C%20shares%20her%20heart-breaking%20story%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20water%20was%20so%20bad%20that%20many%20parts%20of%20the%20body%20were%20completely%20damaged.%20At%20the%20time%20of%20my%20child's%20birth%2C%20the%20doctor%20had%20said%20either%20the%20child%20will%20survive%20or%20the%20mother.%20Three%20years%20later%2C%20we%20came%20to%20know%20that%20he%20can%20neither%20speak%20nor%20hear.%20We%20are%20from%20a%20poor%20family%2C%20we%20face%20a%20lot%20of%20problems.%20Today%2C%20everyone%20in%20our%20house%20is%20sick%20because%20of%20water.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDanu%20Singh%20and%20Aashiya%20are%20among%20the%20many%20parents%20who%20bring%20their%20children%20and%20grandchildren%20suffering%20from%20severe%20health%20issues.%20Most%20of%20these%20children%20cannot%20speak%20or%20hear%20and%20communicate%20through%20gestures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20water%20is%20so%20bad%20that%20the%20food%20is%20not%20digested%2C%20there%20is%20constant%20vomiting.%20Our%20child%20is%20also%20mentally%20very%20weak%2C%20his%20hands%20and%20legs%20do%20not%20move%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAashiya%20adds%2C%20%26quot%3BEver%20since%20my%20child%20was%20born%2C%20he%20has%20been%20mentally%20very%20weak.%20He%20had%20seizures%20in%20childhood.%20He%20is%20very%20weak.%20Sometimes%2C%20he%20has%20fever%2C%20sometimes%2C%20he%20has%20stomach%20pain.%20The%20water%20caused%20so%20much%20trouble%20that%20the%20child's%20liver%20was%20expelling%20water.%20His%20stomach%20had%20become%20as%20hard%20as%20stone.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202014%2C%20the%20United%20Nations%20Environment%20Programme%20(UNEP)%20offered%20to%20assess%20the%20toxic%20waste%2C%20but%20the%20government%20ignored%20the%20offer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKamla%2C%20a%20resident%2C%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20has%20been%2030%20years%2C%20but%20even%20today%20I%20get%20itching%20and%20it%20does%20not%20go%20away%20for%20a%20long%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20resident%2C%20Batham%2C%20recounts%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20facing%20troubles%20ever%20since%20the%20gas%20leak.%20Neither%20do%20we%20get%20proper%20water%2C%20nor%20are%20we%20able%20to%20live%20comfortably.%20Even%20after%20so%20many%20years%2C%20we%20have%20to%20take%20medicines.%20The%20water%20coming%20here%20is%20contaminated%2C%20it%20is%20causing%20many%20diseases.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20whole%20family%20was%20there%20when%20this%20incident%20happened.%20We%20all%20started%20running%20as%20the%20gas%20level%20increased.%20We%20had%20to%20face%20many%20problems%20due%20to%20this%20gas.%20Even%20now%20there%20is%20pain%2C%20burning%20sensation%20in%20the%20eyes%2C%20blood%20pressure%2C%20and%20shortness%20of%20breath.%20Due%20to%20contamination%20of%20water%2C%20there%20was%20pain%20and%20burning%20sensation%20in%20the%20stomach.%20We%20have%20to%20collect%20water%20from%20different%20places.%20My%20grandson%20is%20six%20years%20old%2C%20but%20even%20today%20he%20has%20difficulty%20in%20walking%2C%20sitting%2C%20and%20speaking%20properly%2C%26quot%3B%20shares%20Chandrama%20Devi%2C%20a%20resident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExperts%20believe%20Union%20Carbide%20and%20Dow%20Chemical%20should%20be%20held%20accountable%20under%20the%20Polluter%20Pays%20Principle%20for%20the%20disposal%20of%20this%20toxic%20waste%2C%20but%20no%20action%20has%20been%20taken%20against%20these%20companies%2C%20which%20claim%20they%20are%20not%20subject%20to%20Indian%20courts.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721977260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2F9ggs08s8_bhopal-gas-tragedy_625x300_26_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F40-years-after-bhopal-tragedy-disposal-of-toxic-waste-poses-cancer-threat-6192191%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Forty%20years%20after%20the%20Bhopal%20gas%20tragedy%2C%20its%20toxic%20waste%20cocktail%20is%20brewing%20afresh.%20About%20350%20metric%20tons%20of%20hazardous%20waste%20from%20the%20Union%20Carbide%20factory%20is%20set%20to%20be%20disposed%20of%20at%20the%20Treatment%20Storage%20Disposal%20Facility%20in%20Pithampur%2C%20Indore.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F40-years-after-bhopal-tragedy-disposal-of-toxic-waste-poses-cancer-threat-6192191%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F40-years-after-bhopal-tragedy-disposal-of-toxic-waste-poses-cancer-threat-6192191%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F40-years-after-bhopal-tragedy-disposal-of-toxic-waste-poses-cancer-th