usinessinsider.com%2Fcelebrity-couples-met-blind-dates-2021-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efirst%20met%20at%20Crawford's%20agent's%20wedding%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20early%2090s.%20She%20said%20her%20agent%20did%20not%20want%20her%20to%20go%20to%20the%20wedding%20alone%20and%20gave%20her%20the%20choice%20of%20three%20guys%20to%20take.%20She%20picked%20Gerber.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20wasn't%20a%20setup.%20I%20was%20dating%20someone%2C%20and%20he%20was%20dating%20someone%E2%80%A6%20so%20we%20were%20just%20real%20with%20each%20other%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGerber%20was%20late%20on%20their%20first%20date%2C%20Crawford%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20standing%20in%20the%20lobby%20of%20my%20building%2C%20and%20I'm%20like%2C%20what%20the%20hell%2C%20you're%20late%3F%26quot%3B%20she%20recalled.%20%26quot%3BYou%20know%2C%20and%20I%20have%20a%20bottle%20of%20open%20champagne.%20He%20had%20a%20bottle%20of%20tequila.%20We%20walked%20four%20blocks%2C%20and%20by%20the%20time%20we%20got%20to%20the%20wedding%2C%20we%20were%20like%20best%20friends.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d0586f18-1329-4eee-8756-bbc276937814%5C%22%3EBeing%20friends%20with%20your%20spouse%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbeing-best-friends-with-spouse-benefits-2018-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebenefits%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%202014%20paper%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nber.org%2Fsystem%2Ffiles%2Fworking_papers%2Fw20794%2Fw20794.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENational%20Bureau%20of%20Economic%20Research%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Canada%20found%20that%20those%20who%20named%20their%20spouse%20as%20their%20%26quot%3Bbest%20friend%26quot%3B%20were%20twice%20as%20likely%20to%20have%20higher%20life%20satisfaction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20findings%20are%20based%20on%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Edata%20from%20the%20British%20Household%20Panel%20Survey%2C%20which%20surveyed%20about%2030%2