%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20detailed%20submission%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20the%20state%20government%20said%20that%20the%20directive%20was%20issued%20to%20ensure%20a%20peaceful%20and%20orderly%20pilgrimage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20government%20further%20explained%20that%20the%20directive%20was%20issued%20in%20response%20to%20complaints%20received%20from%20Kanwariyas%20regarding%20confusion%20caused%20by%20the%20names%20of%20the%20shops%20and%20eateries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20yatra%20is%20an%20arduous%20journey%2C%20where%20some%20Kanwariyas%20%2C%20i.e.%20the%20Dak%20Kanwariyas%2C%20do%20not%20even%20stop%20to%20rest%20once%20the%20Kanwar%20is%20on%20their%20shoulders.%20There%20are%20sacred%20features%20of%20the%20pilgrimage%2C%20such%20as%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20Kanwar%2C%20once%20filled%20with%20holy%20Gangajal%2C%20is%20not%20to%20be%20kept%20on%20the%20ground%3B%20nor%20under%20the%20shadow%20of%20the%20gular%20tree.%20It%20may%20also%20be%20noted%20that%20a%20Kanwaria%20embarks%20on%20the%20Yatra%20after%20years%20of%20preparation%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20government%20said%20in%20its%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kanwar%20Yatra%2C%20an%20annual%20pilgrimage%20where%20devotees%20of%20Lord%20Shiva%2C%20known%20as%20Kanwariyas%2C%20travel%20to%20fetch%20holy%20water%20from%20the%20Ganges%20River%2C%20sees%20millions%20of%20participants%20each%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20government%20claimed%20that%20the%20directive%20was%20introduced%20in%20response%20to%20specific%20complaints%20from%20Kanwariyas.%20Pilgrims%20had%20allegedly%20raised%20concerns%20about%20the%20food%20being%20served%20along%20the%20route%2C%20which%20led%20to%20apprehensions%20regarding%20its%20preparation%20in%20line%20with%20religious%20practices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20has%20targetted%20the%20government%20calling%20the%20directive%20'anti-muslim'%20and%20aimed%20at%20creating%20divisions%20within%20the%20