%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20has%20also%20impacted%20the%20water%20supply%20to%20the%20Thane%20Municipal%20Corporation%20(TMC).%20Consequently%2C%20it%20is%20now%20up%20to%20citizens%20to%20take%20action%2C%20both%20individually%20and%20collectively%2C%20particularly%20in%20gated%20communities%20and%20housing%20societies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20relying%20solely%20on%20the%20water%20supplied%20by%20the%20TMC%20and%20purchasing%20additional%20tankers%2C%20the%20residents%20of%20Saprem%20CHS%20decided%20to%20become%20self-sufficient%20in%20their%20water%20needs.%20How%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERead%20on%20to%20find%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20panacea%20for%20water%20woes%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBuilt%20in%201997%2C%20the%20society%20has%20two%20wings%20and%2064%20flats%20in%20total.%20Over%20the%20past%20decade%2C%20residents%20grappled%20with%20major%20water%20shortages.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20several%20days%20when%20we%20had%20water%20supply%20only%20for%20an%20hour%20or%20so.%20We%20also%20had%20to%20call%20for%20a%20water%20tanker%20from%20outside%2C%20paying%20thousands%20of%20rupees%20every%20day.%20It%20was%20a%20very%20difficult%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20Avinash%20Shaligram%2C%20secretary%2C%20Saprem%20CHS%2C%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20problem%20was%20exacerbated%20in%20households%20where%20everyone%20would%20go%20to%20work%20or%20school%20and%20return%20to%20no%20water.%20After%20enduring%20this%20ordeal%20for%20months%2C%20the%20residents%20began%20brainstorming%20and%20coming%20up%20with%20different%20solutions.%20One%20thing%20was%20clear%20%E2%80%94%20they%20wanted%20to%20save%20water%20in%20any%20way%20they%20could.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20society%20has%20a%20water%20tank%20with%20a%20capacity%20of%2020%2C000%20litres.%20As%20they%20started%20breaking%20down%20the%20basics%20of%20water%20usage%20in%20their%20households%2C%20one%20number%20stood%20out%20%E2%80%94%20the%20amount%20of%20water%20used%20in%20the%20toilets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsaprem2-1721819754.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20rooftop%20rainwater%20harvesting%20system%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsaprem2-1721819754.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsaprem2-1721819754-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsaprem2-1721819754-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsaprem2-1721819754-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsaprem2-1721819754-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-358280%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20rooftop%20rainwater%20harvesting%20system%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20found%20that%20every%20time%20we%20flush%20the%20toilet%2C%20it%20uses%20five%20litres%20of%20water.%20In%20a%20household%20of%20four%20members%20who%20each%20use%20the%20washroom%20four%20times%20a%20day%2C%20it%20amounts%20to%2080%20litres%20of%20water%20per%20day.%20For%20the%20entire%20society%2C%20that%20was%20a%20whopping%205%2C120%20litres%20of%20water%20per%20day%2C%20more%20than%201%2F4th%20of%20the%20tank%E2%80%99s%20capacity%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Shaligram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20wondered%20how%20to%20prevent%20this%20natural%20resource%20from%20being%20%E2%80%98flushed%E2%80%99%20down!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20find%20an%20alternative%20water%20source%2C%20they%20conducted%20a%20geological%20survey%20and%20dug%20a%20borewell.%20They%20struck%20water%20350%20feet%20below%20the%20surface%20and%20began%20using%20this%20water%20for%20their%20toilets.%20This%20immediately%20solved%20their%20water%20woes%2C%20providing%20a%2024-hour%20water%20supply!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20stopping%20there%2C%20the%20residents%20sought%20a%20way%20to%20recharge%20the%20groundwater.%20To%20this%20end%2C%20they%20built%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F290271%2Fmumbai-rain-man-makes-rainwater-harvesting-system-using-low-cost-innovation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erainwater%20harvesting%20system%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20rainwater%20that%20was%20being%20collected%20on%20the%20terrace%20was%20going%20to%20waste%2C%20in%20a%20drain.%20We%20wanted%20a%20system%20that%20would%20collect%20this%20water%20and%20divert%20it%20into%20the%20borewell%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Arun%20Deshmukh%2C%20management%20committee%20member%2C%20Saprem%20CHS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20it%20works%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECorrugated%20sheets%20have%20been%20installed%20on%20the%20rooftop%20with%20bars%20on%20the%20side.%20Eight%20pipes%20have%20been%20fixed%20across%20the%20length%20of%20the%20rooftop%20to%20collect%20rainwater.%20These%20pipes%20are%20connected%20to%20pipes%20on%20the%20ground%20that%20channel%20the%20water%20to%20the%20borewell.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstalled%20almost%20three%20years%20ago%2C%20this%20system%20has%20made%20the%20residents%20self-sufficient%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F289205%2Frainwater-harvesting-system-in-tamil-nadu-helps-village-during-cyclone%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprevents%20rainwater%20from%20going%20to%20waste%3C%2Fa%3E.%20They%20have%20been%20using%20this%20water%20for%20their%20toilet%20needs%20and%20are%20now%20exploring%20ways%20to%20use%20it%20for%20other%20purposes.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20the%20water%20tested%20but%20it%20was%20unfit%20for%20other%20use.%20We%20are%20getting%20it%20tested%20again%20now%20to%20see%20if%20it%20can%20at%20least%20be%20used%20for%20washing%20clothes%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Shaligram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESaving%20AC%20Water%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20this%20solution%20produced%20phenomenal%20results%2C%20the%20eager%20residents%20looked%20for%20further%20ways%20to%20save%20water.%20Another%20significant%20source%20of%20water%20wastage%20was%20the%20water%20from%20air%20conditioners%20(ACs).%20Almost%20every%20house%20in%20the%20society%20has%20an%20AC%2C%20says%20Deshmukh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FInfographic-website-25-1721828440.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FInfographic-website-25-1721828440.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FInfographic-website-25-1721828440-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FInfographic-website-25-1721828440-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FInfographic-website-25-1721828440-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FInfographic-website-25-1721828440-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-358388%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20summers%2C%20these%20ACs%20run%20all%20night%20and%20for%20long%20hours%20during%20the%20day%2C%20especially%20on%20weekends%20and%20in%20work-from-home%20situations.%20Generally%2C%20a%20one-tonne%20air%20conditioner%20produces%2010%20litres%20of%20water%20if%20used%20for%20eight%20hours%20%E2%80%94%20with%20this%20amount%20increasing%20based%20on%20the%20size%20of%20the%20AC.%20To%20prevent%20this%20condensate%20(a%20liquid%20obtained%20by%20condensation%20of%20a%20gas%20or%20vapour)%20from%20going%20to%20waste%2C%20Saprem%20CHS%20members%20devised%20a%20method%20to%20save%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20long%20pipe%20runs%20down%20the%20building%2C%20with%20individual%20connections%20to%20each%20house%20to%20collect%20the%20condensate%20from%20their%20air%20conditioners.%20This%20water%20is%20funnelled%20into%20a%20wide%20pipe%20at%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20building%2C%20which%20is%20fitted%20with%20a%20tap%20for%20easy%20access.%20This%20pipe%20can%20hold%20up%20to%2015%20litres%20of%20water.%20This%20water%20is%20used%20to%20water%20the%20plants%20and%20wash%20vehicles%20in%20the%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsaprem-1721820003.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22This%20pipe%20collects%20AC%20condensate%20water%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsaprem-1721820003.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsaprem-1721820003-225x300.jpeg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsaprem-1721820003-500x667.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsaprem-1721820003-768x1024.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsaprem-1721820003-1152x1536.jpeg%201152w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsaprem-1721820003-640x853.jpeg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsaprem-1721820003-150x200.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-358288%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThis%20pipe%20collects%20AC%20condensate%20water%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%2025%20cars%20and%2080%20two-wheelers.%20We%20are%20able%20to%20use%20this%20water%20to%20clean%20them%2C%20effectively%20reusing%20the%20water.%20In%20summer%20months%2C%20we%20also%20use%20it%20to%20water%20the%20plants%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Deshmukh.%20Even%20if%20we%20consider%20that%20it%20takes%20about%2010%20litres%20of%20water%20to%20wash%20a%20car%20and%20five%20litres%20to%20wash%20a%20two-wheeler%2C%20this%20system%20saves%20over%2019%2C000%20litres%20of%20water%20per%20month!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20society%20members%20are%20now%20exploring%20ways%20to%20become%20completely%20self-sufficient%20for%20their%20water%20needs.%20Shaligram%20mentions%20that%20they%20are%20happy%20to%20guide%20other%20societies%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F354201%2Fhow-to-set-up-start-rainwater-harvesting-affordable-system-diy-steps-watch-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eimplementing%20similar%20systems%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20rainwater%20harvesting%20system%20and%20the%20AC%20condensate%20pipes%20each%20currently%20cost%20Rs%201%20lakh%20to%20install.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWater%20is%20a%20finite%20resource.%20We%20need%20to%20save%20it%20in%20whatever%20way%20possible%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESources%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fsmaller-toilet-tanks-could-save-10-of-water%2Farticleshow%2F46843707.cms%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Smaller%20toilet%20tanks%20could%20save%2010%20%25%20of%20water%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%20Published%20On%208%20April%2C%202015%20Courtesy%20Times%20Of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businesstoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Fmumbai-to-face-5-water-cut-from-may-30-10-from-june-5-as-lake-levels-fall-430938-2024-05-26%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Mumbai%20to%20face%205%25%20water%20cut%20from%20May%2030%2C%2010%25%20from%20June%205%20as%20lake%20levels%20fall%E2%80%99%20%3C%2Fa%3EPublished%20On%2026%20May%2C%202024%20Courtesy%20Business%20Today%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721829202000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsaprem2-1721819754.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D358216%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Facing%20severe%20water%20shortages%2C%20residents%20of%20Saprem%20Co-operative%20Housing%20Society%20in%20Thane%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20implemented%20innovative%20water-saving%20measures.%20From%20digging%20a%20borewell%20and%20installing%20a%20rainwater%20harvesting%20system%20to%20reusing%20water%20from%20air%20conditioners%20--%20they%20are%20saving%20thousands%20of%20litres%20of%20water.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Saving%20Kokum%3A%20Why%20a%20Family%20Spent%2015%20Years%20Growing%2010000%20Kokum%20Trees%20%26amp%3B%20Distributed%202%20Lakh%20Saplings%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EKokum%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20rare%20and%20cherished%20sour-tasting%20fruit%2C%20frequently%20features%20in%20the%20cuisine%20of%20people%20living%20in%20the%20Western%20Ghats%20region%20of%20India.%20Despite%20its%20popularity%2C%20this%20savoury%20fruit%20is%20becoming%20increasingly%20scarce%20due%20to%20the%20decline%20in%20its%20plantations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMost%20of%20it%20only%20grew%20wild%20without%20any%20proper%20care%20or%20irrigation.%20They%20were%20almost%20going%20extinct%20when%20my%20father%20started%20to%20grow%20them%20on%20our%20plantation%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ramesh%20Rai%20(68)%2C%20the%20son%20of%20Narayana%20Rai%20%E2%80%94%20a%20farmer%20from%20Ballikan%20village%20in%20Puttur%2C%20who%20was%20one%20of%20the%20first%20people%20who%20realised%20the%20decline%20in%20the%20production%20of%20%3Cem%3Ekokum%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20started%20planting%20the%20fruit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKnown%20scientifically%20as%20Garcinia%20indica%2C%20%3Cem%3Ekokum%20%3C%2Fem%3Eis%20a%20fruit-bearing%20plant%20in%20the%20mangosteen%20family.%20It%20is%20commonly%20found%20in%20the%20Western%20Ghats%20region%20of%20India.%20Devoured%20for%20its%20savoury%20taste%2C%20it%20is%20also%20known%20as%20%3Cem%3Ebheranda%20%3C%2Fem%3Ein%20Marathi%2C%20%3Cem%3Ekudampuli%20%3C%2Fem%3Ein%20Malayalam%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3Ekodampuli%20%3C%2Fem%3Ein%20Tamil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Narayana%20passed%20away%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20his%20family%2C%20especially%20his%20son%2C%20has%20been%20carrying%20forward%20his%20legacy.%20Narayana%E2%80%99s%20estate%2C%20now%20managed%20by%20his%20son%2C%20boasts%20over%2010%2C000%20blooming%20%3Cem%3Ekokum%20%3C%2Fem%3Etrees%20that%20are%20actively%20producing%20fruit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20sat%20down%20with%20Ramesh%20to%20understand%20his%20father%E2%80%99s%20vision%20and%20what%20Ramesh%20is%20doing%20to%20take%20it%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20leap%20of%20faith%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERamesh%20fondly%20recalls%20when%20his%20father%20predicted%20that%20%3Cem%3Ekokum%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewould%20be%20in%20high%20demand%20in%20the%20future.%20Talking%20about%20the%20history%20of%20the%20estate%20and%20his%20father%E2%80%99s%20dream%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20father%20acquired%20our%20property%20in%201950%2C%20transforming%20what%20was%20then%20a%20dense%20forest%20into%20a%20plantation.%20Initially%2C%20we%20planted%20areca%2C%20rubber%2C%20coconut%2C%20jackfruit%2C%20and%20cashew.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Ramesh%E2%80%99s%20father%20was%20farming%20different%20plants%2C%20it%20was%20about%2015%20years%20ago%20that%20he%20began%20planting%20Kokum%2C%20anticipating%20its%20future%20demand%20due%20to%20its%20medicinal%20value.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20started%20growing%20%3Cem%3Ekokum%20%3C%2Fem%3Ebecause%20of%20his%20love%20for%20the%20fruit!%20Furthermore%2C%20%3Cem%3Ekokum%20%3C%2Fem%3Eplants%20don%E2%80%99t%20need%20much%20water%20and%20grow%20well%20in%20the%20local%20climate%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20shares%20that%20his%20father%20planted%20around%2012%2C000%20%3Cem%3Ekokum%20%3C%2Fem%3Eplants%2C%20of%20which%20approximately%2010%2C000%20have%20survived.%20%3Cem%3EKokum%20%3C%2Fem%3Eis%20highly%20sought%20after%20in%20North%20India%20for%20its%20use%20in%20making%20oils%20and%20beverages.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20confident%20that%20the%20price%20of%20%3Cem%3Ekokum%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewould%20rise%2C%20and%20we%20decided%20to%20wait%20for%20the%20plants%20to%20mature.%20Initially%2C%20the%20price%20was%20around%20Rs%2010%20per%20kg%2C%20but%20it%20has%20now%20risen%20to%20Rs%20120%20to%20130%20per%20kg%2C%20and%20in%20some%20places%2C%20it%20can%20go%20up%20to%20Rs%20300%20per%20kg%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20840px)%20100vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-44-1-1721390537.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Narayan%20Rai%2C%20Ramesh's%20father.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-44-1-1721390537.jpg%20840w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-44-1-1721390537-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-44-1-