%5C%22Students%20learning%20farming%20at%20Deesan%20Farms%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fdeesankids-1721657924.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fdeesankids-1721657924-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fdeesankids-1721657924-500x375.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fdeesankids-1721657924-768x576.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fdeesankids-1721657924-150x113.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-357939%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EStudents%20learning%20farming%20at%20Deesan%20Farms%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20farm%2C%20named%20after%20his%20father%2C%20Jagadeeshan%20is%20today%20a%20model%20farm%2C%20visited%20by%20thousands.%20He%20has%20also%20been%20recognised%20by%20the%20Kerala%20Government%20for%20his%20efforts%20in%20organic%20farming.%20He%20has%20been%20awarded%20the%20Kera%20Kesari%20Award%20in%202017%2C%20the%20Yuva%20Kesari%20Award%20in%202019%2C%20and%20the%20Akshayasree%20Award%202022-23%20for%20Best%20Organic%20Farming%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20his%20farm%20was%20set%20up%20and%20started%20running%20smoothly%2C%20he%20was%20filled%20with%20the%20desire%20to%20share%20his%20knowledge%20with%20the%20next%20generation.%20%E2%80%9CMerely%20one%20person%20practising%20a%20sustainable%20model%20of%20farming%20is%20of%20no%20good%20if%20that%20information%20is%20not%20shared.%20I%20wanted%20to%20educate%20other%20farmers%20and%20students%20about%20healthy%20ways%20to%20grow%20food%2C%20consume%20food%20and%20practice%20farming%20that%20is%20beneficial%20to%20all%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaravanan%20conducts%20classes%20for%20the%20Kerala%20Government%20under%20the%20Bhartiya%20Prakritik%20Krishi%20Paddhti%20(BPKP)%20and%20the%20Paramparagath%20Krishi%20Vikas%20Yojana%20(PKVY)%20scheme.%20With%20at%20least%20three%20classes%20per%20week%2C%20he%20claims%20to%20have%20educated%20over%2015%2C000%20farmers%20and%20students%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESreedhu%20P%2C%20agricultural%20officer%2C%20Perumatty%2C%20says%20that%20Saravanan%E2%80%99s%20farm%20is%20a%20perfect%20example%20of%20how%20an%20organic%20farm%20should%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201090px)%20100vw%2C%201090px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fdeesan33-1721657916.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221090%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Saravanan%20turned%20his%20family%20farm%20around%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fdeesan33-1721657916.jpeg%201090w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fdeesan33-1721657916-204x300.jpeg%20204w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fdeesan33-1721657916-500x734.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fdeesan33-1721657916-768x1127.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fdeesan33-1721657916-1046x1536.jpeg%201046w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fdeesan33-1721657916-150x220.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-357938%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESaravanan%20turned%20his%20family%20farm%20around%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20introduced%20comprehensive%20changes%20to%20the%20farm%2C%20including%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F352547%2Ffarmers-income-aneesh-jain-gram-unnati-value-chain-rajasthan-agri-startup%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einstallation%20of%20a%20biodigester%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20improvements%20to%20cow%20management%2C%20culminating%20in%20value%20addition.%20He%20also%20implemented%20a%20solar%20dryer%20for%20post-harvest%20management.%20Students%20and%20farmers%20from%20across%20South%20India%20visit%20his%20farm%20to%20attend%20his%20classes%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sreedhu%2C%20adding%20that%20more%20youngsters%20must%20consider%20this%20path%20instead%20of%20running%20to%20cities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20facing%20a%20nutritional%20crisis%20today%20due%20to%20the%20food%20that%20is%20grown%20and%20consumed.%20The%20younger%20generation%20must%20get%20into%20farming%20and%20go%20back%20to%20the%20way%20things%20were%20done%20before%20%E2%80%94%20organic%20and%20adding%20technology%20where%20needed%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Saravanan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20need%20to%20consider%20that%20while%20we%20focus%20on%20increasing%20our%20bank%20balances%20and%20securing%20our%20children%E2%80%99s%20financial%20future%2C%20we%20are%20only%20providing%20them%20with%20financial%20security.%20What%20about%20ensuring%20their%20food%20security%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%2C%20Images%20Courtesy%20Gnana%20Saravanan%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721658826000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fdeesan-2-1721657645.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D357927%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Gnana%20Saravanan%20and%20Krishnasudha%2C%20IT%20professionals%20in%20Chennai%2C%20left%20their%20corporate%20jobs%20to%20return%20to%20their%20farming%20roots%20in%20Palakkad%2C%20Kerala.%20Over%20the%20past%20eight%20years%2C%20they%E2%80%99ve%20used%20technology%20to%20build%20a%20self-sustaining%20integrated%20farm%20called%20Deesan%20Farms.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22ht