%20%E2%80%9CWe%20work%20towards%20creating%20naturally%20comfortable%20internal%20conditions.%20Our%20goal%20is%20to%20integrate%20nature%20into%20the%20built%20form%2C%20blurring%20the%20gap%20between%20outdoor%20and%20indoor%2C%E2%80%9D%20Swetha%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Titan%20Integrity%20office%20in%20Bengaluru%20is%20a%20prime%20example%20of%20the%20firm%E2%80%99s%20ideology%2C%20but%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20the%20only%20one.%20Karunashraya%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20a%20hospice%20for%20terminally%20ill%20patients%2C%20stands%20out%20as%20a%20significant%20project%20by%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Hindustan%20Unilever%20Research%20Center%20in%20Bengaluru%20further%20showcases%20Mindspace%20Architects%E2%80%99%20commitment%20to%20harnessing%20natural%20forces.%20Swetha%20shares%20that%20its%20courtyards%20and%20verandahs%20seamlessly%20merge%20the%20indoor%20and%20outdoor%20spaces%2C%20allowing%20birds%20to%20fly%20through.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Vellore%20International%20School%20in%20Chennai%20is%20another%20example%20of%20their%20principles%20in%20action.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20designed%20the%20campus%20to%20respond%20to%20Chennai%E2%80%99s%20hot%2C%20tropical%20climate%20by%20orienting%20buildings%20to%20capture%20sea%20breezes%20and%20shield%20from%20the%20intense%20Western%20sun%2C%E2%80%9D%20Swetha%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20layout%20fosters%20a%20dynamic%20learning%20environment%2C%20with%20classrooms%20surrounded%20by%20courtyards%20and%20numerous%20open%20areas%20promoting%20both%20focused%20study%20and%20collaborative%20activities.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EDesigning%20the%20Titan%20Integrity%20office%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opportunity%20to%20design%20the%20Titan%20Integrity%20office%20came%20through%20a%20closed%20competition%20organised%20by%20Titan%20Company%20Ltd%2C%20with%20participation%20from%20six%20architects%2C%20Swetha%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20840px)%20100vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-41-1-1721389363.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20office%20is%20wrapped%20around%20by%20trees%20with%20a%20bio%20lake%20flowing%20through%20it%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-41-1-1721389363.jpg%20840w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-41-1-1721389363-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-41-1-1721389363-500x261.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-41-1-1721389363-768x401.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-41-1-1721389363-150x78.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-357699%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22439%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20office%20is%20wrapped%20around%20by%20trees%20with%20a%20bio%20lake%20flowing%20through%20it%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20presented%20two%20distinct%20options%2C%20and%20the%20company%20selected%20the%20second%20option%20based%20on%20its%20response%20to%20the%20biophilic%20design%20brief%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%20The%20design%20aimed%20to%20foster%20a%20fulfilling%20connection%20with%20nature%2C%20promoting%20health%2C%20fitness%2C%20and%20overall%20well-being.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20central%20concept%20of%20creating%20a%20%E2%80%98bio%20lake%E2%80%99%20influenced%20the%20design.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20bio%20lake%2C%20positioned%20on%20the%20eastern%20side%20of%20the%20site%2C%20harmonises%20with%20the%20natural%20and%20organic%20contours%20of%20the%20existing%20lake%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20The%20office%20buildings%20and%20all%20the%20facilities%20are%20placed%20around%20this%20bio%20lake%20to%20emphasise%20the%20panoramic%20views%20and%20immerse%20users%20in%20a%20peaceful%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20office%20is%20located%20on%20a%206.5-acre%20site%20with%20a%20lake%20on%20the%20eastern%20side.%20The%20design%20takes%20full%20advantage%20of%20the%20site%E2%80%99s%20natural%20features.%20The%20building%20is%20oriented%20in%20such%20a%20way%20that%20its%20longer%20side%20faces%20north-south%2C%20allowing%20glare-free%20natural%20light%20into%20the%20space.%20Porosity%20in%20planning%20and%20form%20allows%20continuous%20movement%20of%20breeze%2C%20ensuring%20natural%20ventilation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESwetha%20also%20emphasises%20that%20she%20focused%20on%20merging%20aesthetics%20with%20sustainability.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20three-floor%20structure%20has%20terrace%20gardens%20at%20every%20level%2C%20reminiscent%20of%20cascading%20rice%20fields%2C%E2%80%9D%20Swetha%20notes.%20The%20terraces%20provide%20insulation%20to%20the%20office%20spaces%20below%2C%20reducing%20heat%20and%20aligning%20with%20the%20concept%20of%20a%20sustainable%20building.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FBpit4xKHeam%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FBpit4xKHeam%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2